Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Epsilon 能量增強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈致動的亞種麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.67,shuoming,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈致動：精神系特異功能的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然優先級比較低
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果捕獲困難的話就只能處決了
