Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那瞬間的記錄模擬出來
